Nollywood actor, Prince Abuchi Ikpo has been found dead in his Asaba apartment in Delta State. The Police Public Relations Officer in the State, DSP Bright Edafe, confirmed his death on Tuesday. Edafe said the actor was killed in his house and locked up till his body was found. “The body was found at his apartment near Jesus Save area, Asaba, on Monday. “They killed him and locked the dead body inside the house. “No much details on this yet,” the PPRO said.